<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      * {
        color: #1e2f50;
      }

      .header {
        width: 100vw;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #1e2f50;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .container {
        width: 100vw;
        max-width: 570px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: white;
        color: #1e2f50;
      }

      .highlight {
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        border-left: 5px solid #00aeff;
      }

      .coupon {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        width: 200px;
        height: 40px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background-color: #4f92dd;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: white;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 220px;
      }

      .eventlist {
        max-width: 550px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .article {
        justify-content: space-between;
        width: fit-content;
        padding: 10px;
      }

      .event-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-direction: column;
        color: #1e2f50;
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      }

      .event-a {
        align-items: flex-start;
        color: #1e2f50;
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      }

      .title {
        font-size: larger;
        text-align: left;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #1e2f50;
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      }

      a {
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: inherit;
      }

      .event-time {
        padding-left: 1rem;
        font-size: smaller;
      }

      .content {
        padding-left: 1rem;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-overflow: ellipsis;
        display: -webkit-box;
        line-height: 18px;     /* fallback */
        -webkit-line-clamp: 3; /* number of lines to show */
        -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
      }

      .content::after {
        content: '...';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        right: 0;
        background-color: white; /* Cor de fundo para esconder qualquer texto atrás dos três pontos */
        padding-left: 5px;
        display: block;
        width: 1.5em;
        height: 1em;
        text-align: right;
      }

      footer {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        padding-top: 1rem;
      }

      .social-media-icon {
        margin-inline: 0.5rem;
      }

      .social-media-icon svg {
        width: 1.5rem;
        fill: black;
      }

      .divider {
        width: 100%;
        height: 2px;
        background-color: #1e2f50;
      }

      .noReply {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #687173;
      }

      .unsubscribe {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #464d4e;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .link-unsub {
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <img class="logo" src="https://praktika.wunderwelt-a.com.br/static/media/praktika-branco.6e03be72.png"/>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <strong>
        Liebe KursteilnehmerInnen
      </strong>
      <p />
      {{#if hasPromotion}}
        <div class="highlight">
          <strong>
            {{message}}
          </strong>
        </div>
        <p />
        {{#with coupon}}
          <text class="coupon">
            {{code}}
          </text>
          <p />
        {{/with}}
      {{/if}}
      <text>Foram lançadas as aulas na PrAktikA das próximas semanas. Acesse a plataforma e confira!</text></br >
      <text>Caso encontre alguma aula que te interesse, se inscreva logo, pois as vagas podem acabar!</text></br >
      <text>Os créditos tem validade de 180 dias para serem usados, então não perca essa oportunidade de aprimorar seu alemão!</text>
      <p />

      <div class="eventlist">
        {{#each mailData}}
          <div id={{id}} class="article">
              {{!-- <header class="event-header"> --}}
              <a class="event-a" href='https://praktika.wunderwelt-a.com.br'>
                ✓ <span class="title"> {{title}}</span>
              </a>
              <br />
              <span class="event-time">{{date}} (horário de Brasília)</span>
              {{!-- </header> --}}
              <p />
              <span class="content">
                  {{description}}
              </span>
          </div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>

      <br />

      <strong>Acesse a PrAktikA!!!</strong>

      <p>Equipe | <strong>PrAktikA - Wunderwelt-A</strong></p>

